text: Hungerbach is a small river of Bavaria, Germany. It is a right tributary of the Altmühl at Dietfurt in Mittelfranken.Topographical maps, Bayerisches Vermessungsamt (BayernAtlas) Retrieved 17 February 2018 ==See also== *List of rivers of Bavaria ==References== Category:Rivers of Bavaria Category:Rivers of Germany
title: Hungerbach (Altmühl)
